channel.title: I'm cracking on!
channel.description:
As you may be aware, the item.java isn't actually updated for the new items, so that's my plan over the next week, to get the whole thing updated, with all new items.
I do have a problem though, even though I updated the pickup code and item code, and everywhere else it said "6540", it won't let me pick items up that are higher than about 7000.
Any ideas?
